.SH NOTES
.SS "Offline Operation"
This scanner is 100% offline and requires no API keys or network access.
All analysis is performed locally for complete privacy.
.SS "False Positive Reduction"
The scanner automatically reduces false positives by detecting:
.IP \[bu] 2
SafeMath usage (skip overflow warnings)
.IP \[bu]
ReentrancyGuard (skip reentrancy alerts)
.IP \[bu]
OpenZeppelin patterns
.IP \[bu]
Solidity 0.8+ (built-in overflow protection)
.IP \[bu]
View/Pure functions
.IP \[bu]
Test/Mock contracts
.IP \[bu]
Commented code
